labels.label:
Online finance: - get csv from project - get company name
-- kafka -- - convert each csv to series of csv - get attributes from json (and rename them) - create json once again, with company_name attribute - publish on kafka 'yfinance' topic
-- out on 'online' directory -- - get date from path - put on HDFS

Online history: - get files from online directory in HDFS (at the end of the day) - create merge key from a company name and a date - merge records into parquet by key - recreate company name and a date from key - put in history directory in HDFS
- remove all directories from 'online' directory once a day (only for clean up purposes)

History Finance: - get data from project - get company name based on directory - get date (yyyy-mm-dd format) based on file name; change filename based on new format - convert csv to parquet - put parquet in HDFS
